WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 13]

01:38.680 --> 01:39.820
I was a bit distracted just now.

01:40.560 --> 01:41.490
Sorry about that.

01:42.790 --> 01:43.330
Alright.

01:44.480 --> 01:45.130
Well,

01:45.680 --> 01:47.770
how did you know I was looking for someone?

01:48.920 --> 01:50.290
I'm sharp as a tack

01:50.310 --> 01:51.180
and always well-informed.

01:53.950 --> 01:56.180
You're the new disciple from Zhuiyu Peak, right?

01:57.310 --> 01:58.570
I heard you have lots of snacks.

01:59.510 --> 02:00.130
Do you have any left?

02:00.310 --> 02:01.260
Share some with me.

02:02.560 --> 02:03.130
Um...

02:03.710 --> 02:04.380
Lifei.

02:07.200 --> 02:07.900
I've given them all out today.

02:08.070 --> 02:08.900
I'll bring some for you next time.

02:10.400 --> 02:12.130
Remember to save some for me next time!

02:12.360 --> 02:13.500
Remember my name!

02:13.750 --> 02:16.730
I'm Deng Xiguang!

02:25.560 --> 02:27.570
I've searched all sixteen peaks.

02:31.870 --> 02:32.890
Senior Brother!

02:33.280 --> 02:34.850
Where are you?

02:35.680 --> 02:36.570
Coming!

02:41.520 --> 02:42.130
What's wrong?

02:42.190 --> 02:43.540
Someone has broken the restriction spell.

02:43.680 --> 02:45.130
Zhaomin wants us to search

02:45.150 --> 02:46.220
for the intruder.

02:51.280 --> 02:52.340
Restriction spell?

03:01.030 --> 03:01.660
Lifei.

03:05.470 --> 03:06.170
Senior brothers!

03:06.400 --> 03:07.380
The intruder is here!

03:07.520 --> 03:08.130
Senior brothers.

03:08.750 --> 03:09.610
The intruder is here!

03:09.870 --> 03:10.500
Senior brothers!

03:10.680 --> 03:11.260
The intruder is here!

03:11.280 --> 03:12.940
The records of disciples' origins from all peaks

03:12.960 --> 03:13.940
are kept in the Huanyue Shrine

03:13.960 --> 03:14.610
behind Wengu Hall.

03:14.870 --> 03:15.690
I'll wait for you there.

03:19.960 --> 03:20.690
Lifei!

03:21.840 --> 03:22.610
Lifei,

03:23.190 --> 03:24.060
where's the intruder?

03:25.360 --> 03:26.380
My mistake.

03:26.520 --> 03:27.220
It was a cricket.

03:28.280 --> 03:29.060
Go back to your duties.

03:29.240 --> 03:30.060
Go... go catch the intruder.

03:31.240 --> 03:31.660
- Go ahead. - Let's go.

04:23.630 --> 04:24.730
You're always running around.

04:25.360 --> 04:26.610
Getting lost elsewhere is one thing.

04:27.000 --> 04:28.610
But if you get lost near Wengu Hall,

04:28.950 --> 04:30.100
the night winds there

04:30.240 --> 04:32.170
might kill you because they're colder than winter frost.

04:32.430 --> 04:33.490
Even the guards won't go there.

04:37.240 --> 04:38.930
Only a fool would wait all night.

04:41.040 --> 04:41.900
He's no fool.

04:42.480 --> 04:43.220
He must have left.

05:34.920 --> 05:38.250
Another pity play. I don't believe it.

06:08.600 --> 06:10.250
Huanyue Shrine is a restricted area for the sect.

06:10.600 --> 06:11.980
Unauthorized disciples are not allowed to enter.

06:13.630 --> 06:14.490
Senior brothers,

06:15.510 --> 06:16.980
I'm here on my master's orders.

06:17.000 --> 06:18.540
I need to look up some sect records.

06:18.950 --> 06:20.700
Oh, you're from Cuihua Peak.

06:21.430 --> 06:22.050
Senior sister,

06:22.360 --> 06:23.930
did Qin send you?

06:25.800 --> 06:26.610
Yes, him.

06:27.720 --> 06:28.490
Then it's fine.

06:28.600 --> 06:29.170
Please come in.

06:29.830 --> 06:30.490
Please.

06:44.240 --> 06:44.810
Who's there?

07:59.950 --> 08:02.050
Hushe Peak.

08:03.630 --> 08:04.660
Hushe Peak?

08:30.510 --> 08:31.340
What are you doing here again?

08:31.720 --> 08:32.930
If you really want to make it up to me,

08:32.950 --> 08:34.100
just stay out of my sight.

08:36.200 --> 08:37.460
I still have something to finish.

08:40.550 --> 08:41.580
What are you plotting now?

08:44.000 --> 08:44.850
Trust me one more time.

08:46.440 --> 08:47.370
Trust you, my foot.

08:47.670 --> 08:48.420
Stop following me.

08:55.320 --> 08:56.010
If we're caught,

08:56.390 --> 08:57.730
we'll both be expelled from Wuyue Court.

11:12.480 --> 11:13.060
Forget it.

11:13.200 --> 11:13.940
I'm going back.

11:14.720 --> 11:15.650
Your master already knows.

11:15.790 --> 11:16.730
Take care of yourself.

11:38.200 --> 11:38.850
Master.

11:39.240 --> 11:41.060
You truly are exceptionally gifted.

11:41.630 --> 11:42.820
In just a few days,

11:43.320 --> 11:45.100
you've been able to break the restriction spells.

11:46.670 --> 11:47.940
I value talent.

11:49.360 --> 11:50.820
But if your mind is distracted

11:51.120 --> 11:52.100
and your conduct is improper,

11:52.750 --> 11:54.580
Yaoguang Peak will not keep you.

11:56.790 --> 11:57.650
I know my mistake.

12:08.740 --> 12:10.250
This is the Danxue secret realm.

12:11.340 --> 12:13.730
Only disciples who have reached the third level of cultivation

12:13.750 --> 12:14.700
can leave here.

12:15.860 --> 12:18.530
What you learned before was broad but not focused.

12:18.980 --> 12:20.420
Your spirit aura is chaotic.

12:20.910 --> 12:22.940
If you can't let go of greed and worldly attachments

12:23.340 --> 12:24.420
and purify your spirit and essence,

12:25.550 --> 12:27.060
you will stay in there for the rest of your life.

12:52.150 --> 12:52.940
Gather the Qi in the vessel

12:53.270 --> 12:54.060
and merge it with heaven and earth.

12:54.080 --> 12:54.940
Transform Qi into spirit

12:54.960 --> 12:55.850
and command all things!

13:17.480 --> 13:18.700
Among Wuyue Court's sixteen peaks,

13:19.000 --> 13:19.940
there is no Hushe Peak.

13:21.200 --> 13:21.770
Right.

13:22.000 --> 13:23.420
None of us has ever seen Hushe Peak.

13:23.960 --> 13:24.580
Lifei,

13:24.790 --> 13:25.940
where did you hear about it?

13:27.870 --> 13:29.980
I've searched every peak

13:30.000 --> 13:31.130
and couldn't find my senior brother.

13:31.150 --> 13:32.060
I'm getting anxious.

13:32.870 --> 13:33.700
Come here.

13:33.750 --> 13:34.180
Here.

13:35.630 --> 13:36.770
Besides

13:37.390 --> 13:39.130
the southwest corner of Baicao Peak,

13:39.150 --> 13:40.530
are there any other peaks?

13:42.440 --> 13:43.460
Never seen one.

13:44.960 --> 13:45.490
Oh,

13:45.840 --> 13:47.370
you haven't been to Cuihua Peak yet, right?

13:49.000 --> 13:51.770
It has never allowed unauthorized entry by disciples of other peaks.

13:52.150 --> 13:54.700
If you want Elder Cuixuan to use Lifei to temper his sword,

13:54.870 --> 13:56.340
by all means, encourage her to go.

14:02.150 --> 14:03.370
The third level of Wuyue Court's techniques.

14:04.150 --> 14:05.060
Spirit energy floods the meridians;

14:05.840 --> 14:06.820
cultivator and sword become one.

14:18.480 --> 14:19.530
The Danxue secret realm

14:20.320 --> 14:21.370
is actually a state of mind.

14:22.550 --> 14:23.490
Unless the inner demon is removed,

14:23.750 --> 14:24.700
the formation will never break.

14:50.200 --> 14:50.980
Inner demon?

15:11.720 --> 15:12.180
Kill.

15:43.630 --> 15:45.770
Did Lei Xiuyuan get punished by his master?

15:49.080 --> 15:49.890
None of my business.

15:50.150 --> 15:50.770
Don't think about him.

16:10.960 --> 16:11.940
The technique is incomplete.

16:12.910 --> 16:13.850
She will still feel pain.

16:29.080 --> 16:31.980
To walk the world is to hold a torch through endless night.

16:32.790 --> 16:34.180
Your goodwill still lingers,

16:34.600 --> 16:35.890
and you are bold and resolute,

16:36.240 --> 16:37.340
so you may break free from this deadlock.

16:37.960 --> 16:39.980
Remember, what your soul yearns for

16:40.360 --> 16:42.300
is the right path for you.

16:43.080 --> 16:44.180
What my soul yearns for?

17:10.830 --> 17:12.810
I was right about you.

17:13.480 --> 17:15.220
You've broken through the third level.

17:15.790 --> 17:18.490
You must have found your heart of cultivation.

17:19.550 --> 17:20.090
Remember,

17:20.720 --> 17:22.570
this heart can overturn heaven and earth.

17:23.070 --> 17:24.620
Even if faced with thunder, fire,

17:24.880 --> 17:25.940
and endless calamity,

17:26.680 --> 17:28.660
it can't be shaken.

17:39.270 --> 17:40.090
- Hello. - Hello.

17:41.350 --> 17:43.330
Heard he broke through the third level in just three days.

17:43.830 --> 17:44.570
Truly impressive.

17:44.920 --> 17:46.010
No wonder Master values him

17:46.110 --> 17:46.940
and took him as a direct disciple.

17:47.270 --> 17:48.460
Truly gifted.

17:48.590 --> 17:49.180
Indeed.

17:50.590 --> 17:51.420
Congratulations

17:51.720 --> 17:52.490
on your advancement.

17:52.830 --> 17:54.290
You've broken through the third level.

17:54.720 --> 17:55.530
Before you,

17:55.750 --> 17:57.980
only Hu Jiaping had done it.

17:58.440 --> 17:59.700
That traitor!

18:00.790 --> 18:02.220
Bewitched by an artifact spirit,

18:02.350 --> 18:04.330
he lost his mind and defied Master.

18:04.480 --> 18:06.900
He's brought shame to Yaoguang Peak.

18:07.590 --> 18:08.570
Well said.

18:09.160 --> 18:09.770
Right.

18:12.590 --> 18:14.330
Hu was Master's direct disciple.

18:14.640 --> 18:15.730
He entered before you.

18:16.480 --> 18:17.420
Speaking ill of your senior

18:17.830 --> 18:18.770
is the same as insulting our master.

18:20.310 --> 18:21.760
[Songfeng, Wuyue Court]
So what if you broke through

18:21.760 --> 18:22.490
the third level?

18:23.240 --> 18:25.810
You must have used some magical treasure, right?

18:26.440 --> 18:28.220
Fine. I'll show you.

18:36.440 --> 18:37.290
Songfeng,

18:37.790 --> 18:38.770
you've been here for years

18:38.790 --> 18:40.140
and still haven't broken through the second level.

18:40.240 --> 18:41.530
Master is already disappointed.

18:42.030 --> 18:44.380
I suggest you watch your words.

18:45.070 --> 18:47.290
Don't upset him further.

18:47.310 --> 18:47.770
You...

18:52.070 --> 18:52.490
Go!

18:53.960 --> 18:54.570
Stop staring!

18:59.510 --> 19:00.900
Songfeng holds grudges.

19:01.110 --> 19:02.530
He probably won't let this go.

19:03.640 --> 19:04.220
Let him.

19:05.550 --> 19:08.420
I thought you had issues with Hu.

19:08.960 --> 19:10.140
Didn't expect you to defend him.

19:14.200 --> 19:15.140
He taught us.

19:16.350 --> 19:17.140
Us?

19:19.550 --> 19:20.290
Jiang Lifei?

19:31.270 --> 19:32.380
Crispy skin, tender meat.

19:32.550 --> 19:33.810
Looks delicious.

19:34.070 --> 19:34.700
Where is Hushe Peak?

19:37.510 --> 19:38.140
Tell me!

19:38.440 --> 19:39.900
I suddenly remembered something.

19:40.160 --> 19:41.730
I have to go right now.

19:42.750 --> 19:43.140
Wait,

19:43.440 --> 19:43.940
can you...?

19:51.480 --> 19:52.220
Master,

19:52.920 --> 19:54.330
when will you be back?

19:55.350 --> 19:57.420
I... I don't know exactly.

19:57.460 --> 19:59.700
But you behave and listen to Zhaomin while I'm gone.

20:01.830 --> 20:03.980
What shameful secret is hidden in there?

20:04.310 --> 20:05.980
Who says Hushe Peak has a secret to...?

20:09.940 --> 20:12.010
There really is a Hushe Peak, isn't there?

20:13.070 --> 20:13.860
Actually,

20:14.110 --> 20:15.330
I know where it is.

20:15.830 --> 20:18.010
There's a map of it in Huanyue Shrine.

20:18.420 --> 20:19.380
Fine.

20:19.660 --> 20:20.460
I guess

20:20.550 --> 20:22.290
no one here can control you anymore.

20:22.500 --> 20:24.420
You've even gone to Huanyue Shrine!

20:26.700 --> 20:27.980
If you won't tell me,

20:29.070 --> 20:30.220
then I'll go myself.

20:30.260 --> 20:31.420
Go ahead then.

20:31.460 --> 20:32.420
It has a restriction spell.

20:32.460 --> 20:33.900
You think you can get in?

20:34.260 --> 20:35.010
Restriction spell?

20:35.750 --> 20:36.530
So mysterious.

20:39.270 --> 20:40.460
Could it be...?

20:43.750 --> 20:45.490
What do you know?

20:48.420 --> 20:49.330
Is there treasure in there?

20:50.220 --> 20:51.220
What treasure, Master?

20:51.260 --> 20:52.050
How much is it worth?

20:52.180 --> 20:54.250
A girl shouldn't be so vulgar.

20:54.700 --> 20:55.620
We'll talk when I get back.

20:58.740 --> 20:59.530
Master.

20:59.700 --> 21:00.490
Tell me now.

21:00.510 --> 21:02.250
Tell me now.

21:03.660 --> 21:05.290
This is urgent.

21:05.310 --> 21:05.980
I'm off!

21:08.900 --> 21:09.730
Master!

21:10.790 --> 21:11.460
Master.

21:21.790 --> 21:23.290
Zhaomin's three-sided mirror.

21:23.460 --> 21:24.860
Master's six-sided mirror.

21:25.270 --> 21:27.490
They should be able to help me break the restriction spell.

22:01.310 --> 22:03.330
Hushe Peak looks like a mallet.

22:40.550 --> 22:41.250
Mr. Hu?

22:41.790 --> 22:42.620
What are you doing here?

22:43.700 --> 22:44.420
Stop looking.

22:46.070 --> 22:47.420
I am your senior brother.

22:53.980 --> 22:54.770
Hold tight.

22:55.420 --> 22:56.220
Or you'll fall.

23:01.220 --> 23:02.140
Senior Brother?

23:06.030 --> 23:07.530
You're really my senior brother?

23:08.510 --> 23:10.090
The one in Master's sketch?

23:11.350 --> 23:12.140
Don't mention that sketch.

23:12.270 --> 23:14.770
I'm handsome and elegant.

23:15.420 --> 23:16.530
I look nowhere near that ugly.

23:17.940 --> 23:19.250
Senior Brother!

23:19.830 --> 23:21.570
Why did you only show up now?

23:22.180 --> 23:23.810
I've been looking for you forever!

23:27.260 --> 23:28.730
You got snot all over my new clothes.

23:29.020 --> 23:30.700
Mu made this for me.

23:30.900 --> 23:31.980
Look at the mess you made.

23:34.510 --> 23:35.700
You're really my senior brother?

23:36.790 --> 23:37.770
Would I lie to you?

23:39.830 --> 23:41.010
Listen to me.

23:41.030 --> 23:42.420
I still can't believe it.

23:44.220 --> 23:45.980
I was an orphan too, just like you.

23:47.260 --> 23:48.490
After that old man took me in,

23:49.070 --> 23:50.980
I followed him, wandering from place to place.

23:51.790 --> 23:53.090
When I grew older

23:53.660 --> 23:55.290
and had learned most of his skills,

23:55.900 --> 23:57.490
he sent me to Chufeng Academy.

23:58.270 --> 24:00.860
Later, I gained the favor of Master Guangwei,

24:01.070 --> 24:02.050
so I went to Wuyue Court.

24:02.590 --> 24:03.660
And you probably know

24:04.220 --> 24:05.220
the rest.

24:06.740 --> 24:08.770
Then why didn't you tell me when I asked before?

24:09.110 --> 24:10.140
You even made things hard for me.

24:11.420 --> 24:12.660
I had no choice.

24:13.030 --> 24:14.420
Master said

24:14.660 --> 24:16.530
I could never mention this to anyone.

24:17.420 --> 24:19.700
Otherwise, both he and I would lose our lives.

24:20.220 --> 24:20.810
And

24:21.030 --> 24:22.250
when did I ever make things hard for you?

24:22.500 --> 24:24.980
That was encouragement and motivation.

24:25.070 --> 24:27.380
I meant well.

24:28.030 --> 24:29.220
I think you had bad intentions.

24:29.590 --> 24:30.810
You just wanted to kick me out of the academy!

24:31.310 --> 24:32.090
You wronged me.

24:32.510 --> 24:34.010
I never wanted to kick you out.

24:34.220 --> 24:35.980
The one I wanted to get rid of was Lei Xiuyuan.

24:38.220 --> 24:38.810
Why?

24:42.460 --> 24:43.090
Because...

24:44.270 --> 24:46.180
Because he clearly doesn't look like a good guy.

24:46.510 --> 24:47.770
I have sharp eyes.

24:47.790 --> 24:49.810
I could tell he had ulterior motives toward you.

24:50.110 --> 24:51.010
See?

24:51.030 --> 24:52.090
You didn't listen

24:52.110 --> 24:52.660
to your elder.

24:52.900 --> 24:54.050
Almost got yourself killed, didn't you?

25:03.680 --> 25:04.220
No.

25:05.000 --> 25:05.530
That's not right.

25:06.400 --> 25:07.620
You're definitely hiding something else from me.

25:08.110 --> 25:09.460
No, really.

25:09.480 --> 25:10.940
Don't overthink things.

25:11.240 --> 25:12.330
You love causing trouble, too.

25:12.480 --> 25:13.420
If it weren't for you,

25:13.640 --> 25:14.250
I wouldn't be

25:14.270 --> 25:15.620
at Wuyue Court this late.

25:15.680 --> 25:16.220
Right?

25:19.480 --> 25:20.050
Jiaping,

25:20.440 --> 25:21.700
do you know where Master is?

25:22.400 --> 25:23.570
Is he being hunted?

25:24.000 --> 25:24.980
Is his life in danger?

25:26.640 --> 25:28.770
Master is a hidden expert.

25:29.310 --> 25:30.730
Ordinary people can't touch him.

25:31.720 --> 25:32.420
An expert?

25:33.680 --> 25:35.090
Why would an expert go into hiding?

25:38.680 --> 25:40.010
He's not some bandit, is he?

25:41.480 --> 25:42.420
Maybe he has too many enemies?

25:44.070 --> 25:44.980
Can't you wish

25:45.000 --> 25:46.980
for something good for our master?

25:47.640 --> 25:49.180
He must have his reasons

25:49.310 --> 25:50.660
for going into hiding.

25:51.240 --> 25:52.530
If you keep looking around blindly,

25:52.680 --> 25:54.570
you'll only bring trouble. Understand?

25:55.480 --> 25:56.330
No.

25:56.750 --> 25:58.490
I need to see with my own eyes that he's safe.

25:59.200 --> 26:00.180
Fine, fine.

26:00.480 --> 26:02.460
I'll find him.

26:02.790 --> 26:05.140
Your top priority now is to focus on your cultivation.

26:05.680 --> 26:07.530
Now that you've become Master Chongyi's disciple,

26:07.960 --> 26:09.090
study hard under him.

26:09.400 --> 26:10.940
Otherwise, even if you find Master,

26:11.350 --> 26:12.530
with your current skills,

26:12.830 --> 26:13.940
you won't be able to help him anyway.

26:15.720 --> 26:18.570
Is that why Master didn't tell me?

26:18.590 --> 26:19.860
Because I can't help?

26:22.790 --> 26:23.380
Jiaping.

26:24.110 --> 26:24.900
I need to get stronger.

26:25.310 --> 26:26.900
One day, I'll be able to help Master.

26:27.070 --> 26:27.660
Good.

26:29.480 --> 26:30.730
Since you show such devotion,

26:31.070 --> 26:33.620
I'll help you.

26:42.110 --> 26:43.770
Your constitution is unique.

26:44.590 --> 26:45.810
So you don't have to follow

26:46.200 --> 26:47.730
the usual methods of cultivation.

26:48.550 --> 26:49.250
Remember,

26:50.200 --> 26:51.250
all spirit energy

26:51.510 --> 26:53.570
is within your every breath.

26:54.240 --> 26:56.810
Nothing is everything. Emptiness is fullness.

27:15.240 --> 27:16.900
Even a flying insect has its own path.

27:17.750 --> 27:18.290
Lifei,

27:18.880 --> 27:20.330
you have a long road ahead.

27:20.920 --> 27:22.140
You'll understand it in time.

27:22.680 --> 27:25.900
Not a word to anyone about what happened today.

27:29.000 --> 27:29.940
I felt it.

27:30.590 --> 27:31.700
Such pure spirit energy.

27:32.310 --> 27:32.730
Jiaping...

27:38.510 --> 27:39.050
Jiaping!

27:40.590 --> 27:41.700
I'm going back to the academy.

27:42.030 --> 27:43.330
Here's the Mind-Calming Mantra for you.

27:44.270 --> 27:45.530
Stay calm through all changes.

27:46.160 --> 27:47.860
Keep your spirit steady and your mind clear.

27:52.440 --> 27:53.860
Just like Master's disciple.

27:54.110 --> 27:55.570
Leaves a letter and disappears. Same bad habit!

27:59.030 --> 27:59.460
Wait,

28:00.790 --> 28:01.770
I don't know the way back!

28:02.200 --> 28:03.490
At least take me back first!

28:04.200 --> 28:04.810
Jiaping.

28:05.510 --> 28:06.810
I don't know the way.

28:07.270 --> 28:08.010
Jiaping!

28:09.790 --> 28:11.700
Jiaping!

28:17.000 --> 28:19.290
Is Zhuiyu Peak to the east or west?

28:28.270 --> 28:29.050
Lifei.

28:34.200 --> 28:34.900
Lifei,

28:35.880 --> 28:36.660
it's you?

28:36.790 --> 28:37.900
Qin?

28:38.070 --> 28:38.810
You're back?

28:40.880 --> 28:41.730
Stop following me.

28:43.680 --> 28:45.490
Aren't you Master Chongyi's disciple?

28:45.920 --> 28:47.050
Why are you here at night?

28:48.880 --> 28:51.140
Are you lost?

28:52.200 --> 28:52.860
Yes.

28:53.720 --> 28:55.810
I thought the moonlight was beautiful

28:56.400 --> 28:57.940
and just wanted to fly in for a closer look.

28:58.240 --> 28:59.810
But the wind was howling,

28:59.830 --> 29:00.660
and I got dizzy

29:00.680 --> 29:01.810
and ended up here.

29:02.270 --> 29:03.090
Wuyue Court

29:03.310 --> 29:04.570
has strong winds and thick fog at night.

29:04.920 --> 29:06.090
Each peak has its own restriction spell.

29:06.310 --> 29:06.980
You can't wander around.

29:09.830 --> 29:11.570
How about I take you back to Zhuiyu Peak?

29:12.640 --> 29:13.530
Okay. Please.

29:13.790 --> 29:15.290
Thank you so much.

29:23.160 --> 29:23.700
Hold tight.

29:35.920 --> 29:37.490
Lifei doesn't trust others easily.

29:39.110 --> 29:40.330
I was worrying for nothing.

29:58.070 --> 29:58.530
Hold tight.

30:25.440 --> 30:27.330
Remember now.

30:29.680 --> 30:30.250
Lifei!

30:36.720 --> 30:37.770
Why those images?

30:38.880 --> 30:39.980
And whose voice was that?

31:06.640 --> 31:07.290
Lifei.

31:08.110 --> 31:08.620
Lifei!

31:09.440 --> 31:10.180
Lifei.

31:11.030 --> 31:11.730
Jiang Lifei!

31:12.200 --> 31:12.570
Jiang...

31:28.750 --> 31:29.730
What's wrong with her?

31:30.240 --> 31:31.180
What's going on here?

31:32.400 --> 31:34.090
Lifei started training at dawn.

31:34.790 --> 31:38.090
Is she finally turning over a new leaf?

31:41.400 --> 31:43.220
No way. Absolutely not.

31:44.480 --> 31:46.860
Jiang Lifei, stop pretending.

31:48.160 --> 31:50.620
Master. You know what?

31:50.880 --> 31:52.530
If it weren't for Qin bringing me back

31:52.550 --> 31:53.380
yesterday,

31:53.400 --> 31:55.090
I might never have seen you again.

31:56.160 --> 31:58.180
If I'm so useless,

31:58.350 --> 31:59.900
that would embarrass you.

32:00.550 --> 32:01.860
For your honor

32:02.640 --> 32:04.660
and for Zhuiyu Peak's dignity,

32:04.920 --> 32:07.050
won't you teach me some self-defense techniques?

32:08.160 --> 32:08.980
Then you...

32:09.240 --> 32:12.940
Um, I'll make you meat buns.

32:14.070 --> 32:16.220
Fine. I'll teach you one.

32:17.550 --> 32:19.220
But let's be clear. Whether you make it or not

32:19.680 --> 32:20.620
depends on you.

32:24.350 --> 32:26.010
Don't just stand there. Go make the food.

32:26.880 --> 32:28.460
Right away. Just a moment.

32:33.510 --> 32:35.290
I went to the place they mentioned last time.

32:35.790 --> 32:36.620
I liked it too.

32:41.790 --> 32:42.660
Lei Xiuyuan!

32:44.510 --> 32:46.700
They say you're Wuyue Court's

32:46.720 --> 32:48.050
once-in-a-century genius.

32:48.270 --> 32:50.490
Since we're both free today,

32:52.590 --> 32:54.220
how about a spar?

32:56.440 --> 32:57.180
Stop right there!

33:16.200 --> 33:17.250
You dare destroy my sword?

33:22.960 --> 33:25.050
Lei, we're fellow disciples.

33:25.240 --> 33:26.050
Let's keep things friendly.

33:26.550 --> 33:27.730
Qin.

33:31.240 --> 33:31.770
Qin.

33:32.680 --> 33:34.140
It's been half a year since we parted at the academy.

33:34.510 --> 33:35.220
I heard

33:35.240 --> 33:36.940
Master Guangwei took you as his personal disciple.

33:37.200 --> 33:37.860
Congratulations.

33:38.680 --> 33:39.770
It's just my master's favor.

33:40.480 --> 33:42.180
Qin, I have things to do.

33:42.350 --> 33:43.140
I'm leaving.

33:49.240 --> 33:50.290
Look at him, so smug.

33:51.030 --> 33:51.810
He struts around

33:51.830 --> 33:53.380
just because he broke through the third level

33:53.480 --> 33:54.620
at Danxue.

33:55.030 --> 33:56.810
He doesn't even respect Qin.

33:58.640 --> 34:01.620
Qin, you're known for your exceptional talent.

34:01.830 --> 34:04.250
You're about to break through the fifth level.

34:05.440 --> 34:07.220
Having a rising star like Lei

34:07.270 --> 34:08.460
is a blessing for Wuyue Court.

34:09.070 --> 34:11.290
Songfeng, I need to see Master Guangwei.

34:11.440 --> 34:12.130
I'm leaving.

34:15.280 --> 34:16.570
If it weren't for Qin,

34:17.030 --> 34:18.130
I'd have taught him a lesson.

34:29.400 --> 34:31.300
Wu Nuo is just an outer sect disciple.

34:32.000 --> 34:33.740
He is of low cultivation, utterly insignificant.

34:34.480 --> 34:36.050
Why did it take you so long

34:36.070 --> 34:37.170
to subdue him?

34:37.670 --> 34:40.610
Sir, that traitor was secretly practicing demonic techniques.

34:40.920 --> 34:41.860
He went mad

34:42.070 --> 34:43.490
and killed his fellow disciples.

34:43.880 --> 34:45.570
He absorbed their spirit power,

34:45.960 --> 34:47.690
which greatly boosted his cultivation.

34:48.400 --> 34:50.090
I had to use my master's

34:50.110 --> 34:51.090
Yin-Yang Tribulation Mirror

34:51.230 --> 34:52.780
to barely restrain him.

34:53.440 --> 34:56.490
How could an immortal sect disciple know demonic techniques?

34:57.000 --> 34:58.090
Have you found out why?

35:06.760 --> 35:10.820
There's no right or wrong in techniques. Power is the only truth.

35:13.150 --> 35:16.300
Think it over. You can hand it in

35:17.360 --> 35:19.010
or not.

35:20.320 --> 35:22.860
I searched for days but found nothing.

35:24.030 --> 35:27.380
Perhaps he was bewitched by the demons.

35:27.840 --> 35:29.210
I've heard of similar incidents

35:29.230 --> 35:30.650
occurring in other sects.

35:31.000 --> 35:34.460
It seems the demons want to overthrow the Central Plains

35:34.960 --> 35:35.980
and divide the immortal sects.

35:38.440 --> 35:39.530
That's possible.

35:40.110 --> 35:41.650
Demons have always been cunning.

35:42.440 --> 35:43.900
With the Sea Calamity approaching,

35:44.280 --> 35:46.420
they will send spies to infiltrate the Central Plains,

35:46.920 --> 35:49.210
spreading confusion and causing trouble.

35:49.840 --> 35:50.300
Yangling,

35:50.840 --> 35:51.980
gather the disciples immediately.

35:52.280 --> 35:53.650
Set up the Demon-Quelling Formation

35:54.550 --> 35:56.130
to secure Wuyue Court.

35:56.760 --> 35:57.340
Also,

35:57.800 --> 35:59.980
strictly screen all inner and outer sect disciples.

36:00.070 --> 36:01.010
Strengthen our defenses.

36:01.480 --> 36:03.460
We mustn't give the demons any opening.

36:04.150 --> 36:04.650
Yes.

36:18.190 --> 36:18.780
Master,

36:19.360 --> 36:20.340
Master Guangwei suspects

36:20.360 --> 36:21.530
it was a demon spy.

36:21.710 --> 36:23.860
He's ordered all peaks to be on high alert against infiltrators.

36:56.880 --> 36:58.090
After all this time,

36:58.630 --> 37:01.530
you still haven't broken through the fifth level.

37:01.840 --> 37:03.300
Useless.

37:03.710 --> 37:06.260
You probably can't even withstand a single strike from the demons.

37:06.960 --> 37:09.780
How can you lead the sect against the Sea Calamity?

37:11.190 --> 37:12.650
How can I possibly

37:12.880 --> 37:15.170
entrust Wuyue Court to your hands?

37:17.480 --> 37:18.300
I am deeply ashamed.

37:18.670 --> 37:20.530
Only the strong may remain on Cuihua Peak.

37:21.030 --> 37:22.610
If you show no improvement,

37:23.360 --> 37:25.690
step down for the younger disciples.

37:26.440 --> 37:27.010
Yes.

37:31.000 --> 37:33.460
Scatter into wind, gather into form.

37:33.480 --> 37:35.090
Draw the essence of heaven and earth,

37:35.280 --> 37:38.380
and fuse the five elemental powers of metal, wood, water, fire, and earth

37:38.400 --> 37:39.380
into your vessel.

37:40.230 --> 37:43.050
Release different techniques according to subtle variations,

37:43.070 --> 37:45.210
and you will have endless transformations.

37:45.800 --> 37:49.650
This is the Earth-Shattering Five Turtles Technique.

38:26.880 --> 38:28.780
Master! Did you see that?

38:29.360 --> 38:30.490
I can use the water technique now.

38:33.880 --> 38:34.650
Well...

38:35.400 --> 38:36.460
I taught you for so long,

38:36.480 --> 38:39.010
and you've only just managed to fuse your water and wood spirits.

38:39.550 --> 38:41.050
I'm a bit ashamed, honestly.

38:41.510 --> 38:42.490
The hard part is still ahead.

38:42.800 --> 38:45.460
Especially the metal technique. That's the foremost of the five elements.

38:46.000 --> 38:46.780
Take your time practicing.

38:48.150 --> 38:49.300
As I always say,

38:49.440 --> 38:51.090
I've taught you everything.

38:51.670 --> 38:53.490
Whether you succeed is all up to you.

39:04.480 --> 39:06.340
Where... where did it go?

39:09.280 --> 39:10.210
Where did it go?

39:11.360 --> 39:12.460
What happened, Master?

39:19.320 --> 39:20.380
Take your time practicing.

39:20.960 --> 39:22.260
I'm going back to sleep.

39:28.190 --> 39:30.130
Practice all you want, but don't forget to cook.

39:30.920 --> 39:31.650
Got it.

39:32.110 --> 39:33.380
You're still eating while you talk.

39:59.320 --> 40:01.010
How am I supposed to use this metal spirit?

40:38.400 --> 40:38.690
I...

40:39.400 --> 40:40.650
I mastered the metal technique?

41:38.760 --> 41:42.440
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

41:42.760 --> 41:45.260
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

41:45.720 --> 41:49.040
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

41:49.280 --> 41:51.480
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

41:52.520 --> 41:56.000
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

41:56.720 --> 41:59.080
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

41:59.680 --> 42:01.200
♪No calamity can rival♪

42:01.600 --> 42:04.640
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

42:06.780 --> 42:10.260
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

42:11.020 --> 42:13.260
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

42:14.070 --> 42:15.010
What do you want?

42:15.010 --> 42:16.740
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

42:17.380 --> 42:19.660
♪Past the pagoda♪

42:20.460 --> 42:22.510
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

42:22.510 --> 42:23.210
Your spirit energy.

42:24.300 --> 42:26.580
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

42:27.100 --> 42:30.060
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

42:30.780 --> 42:32.980
♪Reign supreme♪

42:34.060 --> 42:37.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

42:38.960 --> 42:39.690
Take it back.

42:40.320 --> 42:41.380
Never show your face before me again.

42:42.160 --> 42:43.360
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:43.360 --> 42:44.760
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:56.800 --> 42:59.740
♪It's me, blinded by longing♪

42:59.900 --> 43:02.700
♪Every glance lands on you♪

43:02.860 --> 43:07.980
♪Fire and water clash, yet we cling inseparably♪

43:08.420 --> 43:11.260
♪Lotus broken, threads still bind us♪

43:11.580 --> 43:14.580
♪My heart calm till you stir storms and rain♪

43:15.220 --> 43:18.500
♪You are my destined rival♪

43:19.660 --> 43:24.620
♪Winters pass, springs come; bound for lifetimes, fate ties me to you♪

43:25.420 --> 43:30.740
♪Mountains, rivers, lakes and seas, I follow no one but you♪

43:31.300 --> 43:37.260
♪Bitterness brews sweet bliss, drained in one sip♪

43:37.700 --> 43:43.020
♪Love and feud balance out, I'm yours alone♪

43:43.140 --> 43:48.740
♪Fated foes, fate plays tricks; you complete my five elements♪

43:48.820 --> 43:54.420
♪If you don't leave, I'll never abandon you♪

43:54.580 --> 44:00.620
♪If you don't leave, I'll never abandon you♪

44:01.060 --> 44:09.580
♪We'll dwell in mortal dust, stay side by side till the end♪

44:18.820 --> 44:21.540
♪Sometimes I throw petty fits♪

44:21.820 --> 44:24.580
♪I blame all troubles on you♪

44:24.780 --> 44:29.900
♪Though distant on the surface, our souls resonate as one♪

44:30.340 --> 44:33.220
♪We wander far, parted to separate corners♪

44:33.500 --> 44:36.460
♪Yet my heart still leans toward you, my foe♪

44:37.140 --> 44:40.420
♪I sigh and laugh, defeated in this game of affection♪

44:41.660 --> 44:46.620
♪Winters pass, springs come; bound for lifetimes, fate ties me to you♪

44:47.340 --> 44:52.660
♪Mountains, rivers, lakes and seas, I follow no one but you♪

44:53.220 --> 44:59.180
♪Perhaps endless tangling is our silent bond♪

44:59.620 --> 45:04.940
♪Love and feud balance out, I'm yours alone♪

45:05.060 --> 45:10.660
♪Fated foes, fate plays tricks; you complete my five elements♪

45:10.740 --> 45:16.340
♪Burning love, unbridled hatred, they suit each other well♪

45:16.500 --> 45:22.580
♪If you don't leave, I'll never abandon you♪

45:23.180 --> 45:32.380
♪We'll dwell in mortal dust, stay side by side till the end♪
